(Gu Yixiao)

00:01:24.780 --> 00:01:27.380
(Gu Yixiao)

00:01:40.160 --> 00:01:41.080
You're scared.

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:43.840
Of course I am.

00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:45.480
It's pitch dark.

00:01:45.880 --> 00:01:47.440
