The power is out,

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:09.720
so I called them.

00:02:11.320 --> 00:02:12.160
Ye Xingwan,

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:13.480
let me ask you one more time.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:15.200
What are you doing in my study?

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:18.240
I told you, I came here
to find a candle.

00:02:20.640 --> 00:02:22.040
I just left Haicheng

00:02:22.040 --> 00:02:23.360
and the power went out.

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:25.740
That can't just be a coincidence, right?

