allows three chances
to enter the wrong password.

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:39.920
If you already tried just now,

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:41.320
then the remaining tries

00:02:41.600 --> 00:02:42.880
will be reduced accordingly.

00:02:49.820 --> 00:02:50.860
(Gu Yixiao)

