This is Villa No. 1.

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:26.320
I report the outage for repair.

00:03:32.120 --> 00:03:34.120
I called for repairs before you came in.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:35.760
It should be fixed by now.

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:37.880
