00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:14.840
I guess I misunderstood.

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:16.520
Sorry about that.

00:04:16.920 --> 00:04:18.360
(He does know how to apologize.)

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:21.000
(Looks like Wang Yaqin really
understands him.)

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:29.480
It's almost midnight.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:32.520
Are you hungry?

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:36.070
I'll make you a bowl of noodles.

00:04:46.440 --> 00:04:47.440
Eat it while it's hot.

00:04:59.640 --> 00:05:00.840
Why this noodle?

00:05:01.760 --> 00:05:03.200
Isn't today your birthday?

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:07.120
Happy birthday,

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:08.640
Gu Yixiao.

00:05:30.280 --> 00:05:31.640
Coriander noodles?

00:05:32.080 --> 00:05:33.280
That's not common, right?

00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:36.080
He loves it?

00:05:37.080 --> 00:05:38.560
Yeah, he really does.

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:40.480
I can teach you.

00:05:41.240 --> 00:05:42.080
Give it a try.

00:05:58.840 --> 00:05:59.840
If you like it,

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:01.480
I'll make it for you often.

00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:08.040
Ye Xingwan,

00:06:08.220 --> 00:06:09.330
stop thinking you're clever.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:11.640
Don't waste time on these things.

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:25.640
Happy birthday.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.000
If you like it,

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:28.320
I'll make it for you often.

