00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:17.080
(must endure every hardship.)

00:08:43.560 --> 00:08:45.720
Xingwan, you scared me to death
yesterday.

00:08:45.960 --> 00:08:47.960
I almost rushed over to find you.

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:49.800
I'm sorry, Qianyu.

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:51.920
