00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:10.960
What about you?

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.560
Will he treat you the same way?

00:09:13.160 --> 00:09:14.280
I can't leave just yet.

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:15.520
But don't worry.

00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:17.000
I'll make sure I'm safe.

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:20.320
On his birthday banquet,

00:09:20.330 --> 00:09:21.880
