00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:49.640
Hello? Xingyue.

00:09:50.280 --> 00:09:51.920
It's Yixiao's birthday today.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:53.720
Let me handle the gift for you.

00:09:54.960 --> 00:09:55.960
OK.

